OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776927916
OL,3,COfficer injured in crash which killed
OL,4,Ccolleague is released from hospital
OL,6,FThe incident involved a marked Ford
OL,7,FFocus police car and a VW Scirocco.
OL,9,FThe collision happened on the
OL,10,Fwestbound A20 London Road at the
OL,11,Fjunction with Button Street,
OL,12,FFarningham at approximately 7.45pm on
OL,13,FThursday 19 March.
OL,15,FIn a tribute, PC Corke's family
OL,16,Fdescribed him as "our beautiful boy"
OL,17,Fand "one of the finest young men ever
OL,18,Fto have walked this earth"
OL,20,FKent Police held a two-minute silence
OL,21,Ffollowing his death.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
